                <p dir="ltr">Ninja Gaiden 4 launches on October 20 for Xbox Series X|S, PS5, PC, and Game Pass. The fourth entry in the long-running action game series is developed in collaboration with Koei Tecmo's Team Ninja and Platinum Games, best known for titles like Bayonetta and Nier: Automata. The game will follow long-time Ninja Gaiden protagonist Ryu Hayabusa and a new character, Yakumo--who is a member of the Hayabusa Clan's rivals, the Raven Clan. The duo will battle against the forces of the Dark Dragon, who has plunged Tokyo into a permanent storm known as the Rain of Rot. If you're eager to get your hands on Ninja Gaiden 4, a <a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?fntitle=Ninja+Gaiden+4+Preorders+Are+Live%2C+Supports+Play+Anywhere+On+Xbox+And+PC&amp;fnauthor=brendanhesse&amp;fndate=2025-06-10+15%3A49%3A00&amp;fnupdated=2025-06-10+16%3A14%3A36&amp;fnarticle_id=6532333&amp;fntype1=Games&amp;fntype2=News&amp;fntype3=Pre-Order+Guides&amp;q=https%3A%2F%2Fbestbuy.7tiv.net%2FZ645Q0&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fninja-gaiden-4-preorders-are-live-supports-play-anywhere-on-xbox-and-pc%2F1100-6532333%2F&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">$70 standard edition</a> and a <a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?fntitle=Ninja+Gaiden+4+Preorders+Are+Live%2C+Supports+Play+Anywhere+On+Xbox+And+PC&amp;fnauthor=brendanhesse&amp;fndate=2025-06-10+15%3A49%3A00&amp;fnupdated=2025-06-10+16%3A14%3A36&amp;fnarticle_id=6532333&amp;fntype1=Games&amp;fntype2=News&amp;fntype3=Pre-Order+Guides&amp;q=https%3A%2F%2Fbestbuy.7tiv.net%2FVxV9mJ&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fninja-gaiden-4-preorders-are-live-supports-play-anywhere-on-xbox-and-pc%2F1100-6532333%2F&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">$90 Deluxe Edition</a> are both up for preorder at multiple online retailers. Securing a copy early also gets you a special in-game costume as a preorder bonus.</p><h2 dir="ltr">Ninja Gaiden 4 Preorder Bonus</h2><figure data-align="center" data-size="large" data-img-src="https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1701/17013431/4511234-ng4preorderbonus.jpg" data-ref-id="1300-4511234" data-ratio="0.5625" data-width="1280" data-embed-type="image"><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1701/17013431/4511234-ng4preorderbonus.jpg" data-ref-id="1300-4511234"></a><figcaption>Ninja Gaiden 4 preorder bonus</figcaption><img src="https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1701/17013431/4511234-ng4preorderbonus.jpg"></figure><p dir="ltr">All Ninja Gaiden 4 preorders include the Dark Dragon Descendant skin for Yakumo as an exclusive extra. The skin will be available at launch. Physical and digital preorders are both eligible for the preorder bonus.</p><div title="6532333 - Ninja Gaiden 4 preorders" data-embed-type="buylink" data-ref-id="3683" data-template="4" data-size="buylink__listicle" data-title="6532333 - Ninja Gaiden 4 preorders" data-collection="">                                                                     <div>             <h2>                    <a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?fntitle=Ninja+Gaiden+4+Preorders+Are+Live%2C+Supports+Play+Anywhere+On+Xbox+And+PC&amp;fnauthor=brendanhesse&amp;fndate=2025-06-10+15%3A49%3A00&amp;fnupdated=2025-06-10+16%3A14%3A36&amp;fnarticle_id=6532333&amp;fntype1=Games&amp;fntype2=News&amp;fntype3=Pre-Order+Guides&amp;q=https%3A%2F%2Fbestbuy.7tiv.net%2FZ645Q0&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fninja-gaiden-4-preorders-are-live-supports-play-anywhere-on-xbox-and-pc%2F1100-6532333%2F&amp;event_type=click" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/clicks.trx-hub.com\/xid\/fandom_32094_gamespot?fntitle=Ninja+Gaiden+4+Preorders+Are+Live%2C+Supports+Play+Anywhere+On+Xbox+And+PC&amp;fnauthor=brendanhesse&amp;fndate=2025-06-10+15%3A49%3A00&amp;