ever, the specific format differs based on the platform you're buying for. The PS5 version includes a game disc in the box, while the Xbox version is a code in a box. There are also preorders for a "physical" PC version that are just a code voucher for the Windows version. It's worth noting that Xbox or Windows versions support Xbox Play Anywhere, meaning you're actually getting both Xbox and Windows versions, plus the ability to play on mobile via cloud streaming.</p><p dir="ltr">Digital preorders are also available on all platforms, including a Steam version--but this is different from the Windows Store version, and only includes a key to play on Steam.</p><p dir="ltr"><strong>Ninja Gaiden 4 Standard Edition Physical Preorders:</strong></p><ul><li dir="ltr"><a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?fntitle=Ninja+Gaiden+4+Preorders+Are+Live%2C+Supports+Play+Anywhere+On+Xbox+And+PC&amp;fnauthor=brendanhesse&amp;fndate=2025-06-10+15%3A49%3A00&amp;fnupdated=2025-06-10+16%3A14%3A36&amp;fnarticle_id=6532333&amp;fntype1=Games&amp;fntype2=News&amp;fntype3=Pre-Order+Guides&amp;q=https%3A%2F%2Fbestbuy.7tiv.net%2FZ645Q0&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fninja-gaiden-4-preorders-are-live-supports-play-anywhere-on-xbox-and-pc%2F1100-6532333%2F&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">PS5</a> -- $70 | Also <a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?fntitle=Ninja+Gaiden+4+Preorders+Are+Live%2C+Supports+Play+Anywhere+On+Xbox+And+PC&amp;fnauthor=brendanhesse&amp;fndate=2025-06-10+15%3A49%3A00&amp;fnupdated=2025-06-10+16%3A14%3A36&amp;fnarticle_id=6532333&amp;fntype1=Games&amp;fntype2=News&amp;fntype3=Pre-Order+Guides&amp;q=https%3A%2F%2Fgoto.walmart.com%2Fc%2F1804712%2F565706%2F9383%3Fveh%3Daff%26sourceid%3Dimp_000011112222333344%26u%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.walmart.com%2Fip%2FMustang-Standard-Edition%2F16731807776%26subId1%3Dsubid_value&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fninja-g